class.name: SiMMLSequencer
class.description: It is responsible for creating a sequence of commands which control the sound generation. You can think of it as a parsed and expanded representation of an MML string. [b]Warning:[/b] This class currently has no intended use in the API. If you need this class and its unexposed methods in your project, please [b][url=https://github.com/YuriSizov/gdsion/issues]create a feature request with your use case[/url][/b]!
